is this what you followed? https://onnxruntime.ai/docs/build/eps.html#onednn
we have another example you can play with - https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/blob/master/tools/ci_build/github/azure-pipelines/linux-dnnl-ci-pipeline.yml
It's not supported in a minimal build. What's the reason you added the `--minimal_build` flag?

> It's not supported in a minimal build. What's the reason you added the `--minimal_build` flag?

because I got error without `--minimal_build` flag,
the error as ### https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime/issues/11547
I updated the gcc version to 10.2, but it does not work either
